WEBVTT

00:11.010 --> 00:13.940
[Tangjing, Capital of Biantang]

00:14.640 --> 00:15.440
Your Majesty.

00:16.830 --> 00:17.350
Beauties.

00:17.350 --> 00:18.670
-Your Majesty.
-Your Majesty, come here.

00:18.670 --> 00:19.550
Come here, Your Majesty.

00:19.550 --> 00:20.960
-I'm right here.
-Where are you?

00:20.960 --> 00:22.000
Catch me.

00:22.000 --> 00:23.640
I'll surely catch you.

00:25.230 --> 00:26.030
Come here.

00:26.870 --> 00:27.830
Over here.

00:28.050 --> 00:31.440
[Li Jiao, Biantang Emperor]

00:29.350 --> 00:31.210
You won't catch me, Your Majesty.

00:31.640 --> 00:32.240
Your Majesty.

00:32.240 --> 00:33.700
-Your Majesty.
-Hurry up.

00:34.070 --> 00:34.560
Come here,

00:34.560 --> 00:35.520
beauties.

00:37.430 --> 00:38.670
You run really fast.

00:39.430 --> 00:40.840
Your Majesty, I'm here.

00:40.840 --> 00:42.470
-Your Majesty.
-Come here, Your Majesty.

00:42.470 --> 00:42.880
Come here.

00:42.880 --> 00:44.610
-Come and catch me.
-Come here.

00:47.390 --> 00:48.200
Your Majesty.

02:17.110 --> 02:22.120
[REBIRTH]

02:22.560 --> 02:25.130
[Episode 6]

02:35.340 --> 02:37.440
[Biantang Empress]

02:37.000 --> 02:38.310
Spare us, Your Majesty!

02:38.310 --> 02:39.000
-Spare us, Your Majesty!
-Spare us, Your Majesty!

02:39.000 --> 02:41.870
-Spare us, Your Majesty!
-Spare us, Your Majesty!

02:41.870 --> 02:43.310
-Spare us, Your Majesty!
-Spare us, Your Majesty!

02:43.310 --> 02:44.630
-Spare us!
-Spare us!

02:44.630 --> 02:45.800
It's not your fault.

02:46.360 --> 02:48.820
You couldn't disobey the Emperor's orders.

02:49.000 --> 02:49.910
Chief Fang,

02:50.360 --> 02:51.430
let them leave.

02:52.120 --> 02:53.400
The floor is too cold.

02:54.000 --> 02:56.710
Kneeling too long will harm their health.

02:57.079 --> 02:57.680
Yes,

02:58.079 --> 02:59.030
Your Majesty.

02:59.630 --> 03:00.590
Get up now.

03:04.910 --> 03:07.840
-Thank you, Your Majesty.
-Thank you, Your Majesty.

03:12.190 --> 03:12.910
Physician,

03:13.400 --> 03:14.710
how is His Majesty?

03:15.560 --> 03:16.680
Your Majesty,

03:17.280 --> 03:19.340
His Majesty has liver qi stagnation,

03:19.430 --> 03:20.829
poor blood circulation,

03:20.910 --> 03:22.800
and cold invasion,

03:22.960 --> 03:25.190
which caused sudden hematemesis.

03:25.190 --> 03:26.150
Is there a cure?

03:26.590 --> 03:27.280
Yes,

03:27.470 --> 03:29.800
but His Majesty needs to drink less wine

03:30.190 --> 03:31.120
and rest more,

03:31.350 --> 03:33.310
so he can recover quickly.

03:33.470 --> 03:35.360
Go and arrange the medicinal diet.

03:35.360 --> 03:35.960
Yes.

03:43.960 --> 03:44.760
Your Majesty.

03:48.030 --> 03:49.560
Did you hear, Your Majesty?

03:49.750 --> 03:50.810
The physician said

03:51.500 --> 03:52.840
it's not a big problem.

03:53.430 --> 03:56.360
It's probably related
to the cold weather recently.

03:56.360 --> 03:57.760
Just rest, Your Majesty.

03:58.590 --> 04:00.790
Do not overthink or overwork yourself.

04:03.960 --> 04:05.190
All these years,

04:05.870 --> 04:07.680
you've shielded me from so much,

04:08.150 --> 04:11.750
running back and forth
between the imperial court and the harem.

04:12.080 --> 04:13.740
It's been really hard for you.

04:16.040 --> 04:17.750
Your Majesty, to share your burdens

04:17.750 --> 04:19.120
is my blessing.

04:20.269 --> 04:22.330
Hardships are not worth mentioning.

04:24.070 --> 04:25.330
It's been hard for you.

04:57.270 --> 04:58.830
His Majesty's health

04:59.270 --> 05:00.800
is getting worse day by day.

05:01.430 --> 05:03.090
He vomited blood again today.

05:03.390 --> 05:05.650
Then what do you plan to do, Your Majesty?

05:08.230 --> 05:10.470
The two beauties you sent to His Majesty

05:10.630 --> 05:11.480
are very good.

05:12.120 --> 05:13.780
He fell in love at first sight.

05:14.680 --> 05:17.720
Continue to select some beautiful women

05:17.920 --> 05:19.580
and send them into the palace,

05:19.870 --> 05:21.830
just to make His Majesty happy.

05:22.750 --> 05:23.870
I understand.

05:30.510 --> 05:32.909
[Zhan Ziyu, Empress's Male Favorite]

05:39.070 --> 05:39.870
Your Majesty,

05:41.390 --> 05:42.720
there is another thing.

05:43.360 --> 05:45.690
His Highness has returned from Great Yan.

05:45.920 --> 05:46.720
And

05:47.650 --> 05:50.240
he brought a woman
of unknown origin with him.

05:51.770 --> 05:53.600
Who is she?

05:53.870 --> 05:55.240
I do not know yet,

05:56.430 --> 05:58.340
but it is better to be careful.

05:59.270 --> 06:01.920
After all, the Crown Prince
is growing more powerful by the day.

06:01.920 --> 06:04.520
If he develops
disloyal thoughts towards you,

06:05.120 --> 06:06.600
that would not be good.

06:09.160 --> 06:10.760
Then you will act on my behalf

06:12.040 --> 06:14.430
to find out her identity.

06:20.790 --> 06:21.390
Yes.

06:36.600 --> 06:38.530
You have accompanied me for 3 days.

06:38.600 --> 06:41.070
Why don't you ask who I am

06:42.040 --> 06:43.800
and why I wanted to jump into the lake?

06:43.800 --> 06:44.860
In this vast world,

06:45.190 --> 06:46.990
everyone has their own sorrows.

06:47.630 --> 06:49.900
If you don't want to say, I won't ask.

07:15.070 --> 07:16.750
You remind me of someone.

07:22.600 --> 07:23.360
That person

07:23.950 --> 07:25.610
must be very important to you.

07:26.480 --> 07:27.160
Yes.

07:29.070 --> 07:30.040
Very important.

07:30.960 --> 07:32.820
But he never wants to see me again,

07:33.510 --> 07:35.070
and I can't forget him.

07:35.870 --> 07:38.600
Then can you temporarily
treat me as that person,

07:38.870 --> 07:40.360
until you truly forget him

07:40.830 --> 07:42.230
and are no longer in pain?

08:13.560 --> 08:14.270
Can I?

08:17.560 --> 08:18.490
Can I forget him?

08:19.800 --> 08:21.260
As long as you are willing,

08:21.560 --> 08:23.120
I can always accompany you.

08:55.430 --> 08:57.950
[Crown Prince's Mansion, Biantang]

09:08.550 --> 09:09.150
Come.

09:12.200 --> 09:12.790
Careful.

09:14.550 --> 09:15.480
Here, hold this.

09:32.790 --> 09:33.480
Li Ce.

09:34.200 --> 09:35.870
This is the Crown Prince's Mansion?

09:35.870 --> 09:37.270
Why does it feel so weird?

09:37.670 --> 09:38.270
Qiao,

09:38.390 --> 09:39.760
I can't explain it in one sentence.

09:39.760 --> 09:41.000
I'll explain it to you later.

09:41.000 --> 09:41.930
Follow me first.

09:47.360 --> 09:47.910
Hurry.

09:48.830 --> 09:49.630
Come in first.

09:56.320 --> 09:56.870
Qiao,

09:57.080 --> 09:58.240
these are all the beautiful clothes

09:58.240 --> 09:59.970
I brought back from my travels.

10:02.000 --> 10:02.830
So revealing.

10:04.470 --> 10:05.730
Unbearable to look at.

10:08.030 --> 10:10.030
These clothes don't even cover the body.

10:10.030 --> 10:10.600
I can't wear them.

10:10.600 --> 10:11.240
Qiao,

10:11.240 --> 10:12.440
I didn't mean that.

10:12.470 --> 10:13.480
It's an emergency.

10:13.480 --> 10:14.840
I'll explain it to you later, okay?

10:14.840 --> 10:15.360
Come.

10:16.600 --> 10:17.460
Your Highness,

10:17.840 --> 10:18.600
it's bad.

10:18.720 --> 10:19.750
We just entered the mansion,

10:19.750 --> 10:20.720
and Her Majesty already knows.

10:20.720 --> 10:21.970
Someone from the palace has arrived,

10:21.970 --> 10:23.510
asking you to enter the palace
immediately to pay your respects.

10:23.510 --> 10:24.870
I've been away for months,

10:24.870 --> 10:25.440
but Mother

10:25.440 --> 10:26.950
is as well-informed as ever.

10:26.950 --> 10:27.790
It doesn't matter.

10:27.790 --> 10:28.750
I will go right now.

10:28.750 --> 10:29.240
Okay.

10:30.240 --> 10:31.360
Here, Qiao.

10:32.870 --> 10:33.730
Your Highness.

10:34.270 --> 10:36.130
Remember to change your clothes.

10:41.100 --> 10:42.630
Greetings, Your Highness.

11:14.670 --> 11:16.750
I'm Zhan Ziyu, Grand Minister of Rites,

11:16.750 --> 11:18.810
acting on Her Majesty's oral decree.

11:19.080 --> 11:21.190
His Highness has been traveling
for a long time.

11:21.190 --> 11:23.050
Her Majesty misses him very much.

11:23.630 --> 11:24.870
She personally sent us

11:24.870 --> 11:28.000
to present His Highness
with 10 pieces of deer skin glue,

11:28.080 --> 11:29.480
5 boxes of Baiyi incense,

11:29.910 --> 11:31.490
and 5 wild ginsengs,

11:31.940 --> 11:34.110
to condition His Highness's body.

11:35.240 --> 11:38.370
These items are all personally
bestowed by Her Majesty.

11:39.390 --> 11:40.910
You must deliver them to His Highness

11:40.910 --> 11:43.170
and place them properly inside the hall.

11:43.320 --> 11:45.150
If there is any mistake,

11:45.550 --> 11:47.080
you will not be forgiven.

11:47.550 --> 11:48.210
-Yes.
-Yes.

12:17.670 --> 12:18.600
Who is in there?

12:23.270 --> 12:24.030
Your Highness,

12:24.030 --> 12:26.030
this person looks a bit unfamiliar.

12:29.510 --> 12:30.600
You are from Fengyi Palace?

12:30.600 --> 12:32.550
Why have I never seen you
at Her Majesty's place?

12:32.550 --> 12:33.360
Your Highness,

12:33.360 --> 12:35.090
I am a subordinate of Lord Zhan.

12:39.000 --> 12:39.870
Your Highness, Your Highness!

12:39.870 --> 12:40.800
I have a stomachache.

12:40.800 --> 12:42.530
I need to return to the mansion.

12:46.550 --> 12:47.680
Catch the assassin!

12:55.550 --> 12:57.630
An assassin has indeed infiltrated
the Crown Prince's Mansion

12:57.630 --> 12:58.830
to harm His Highness.

13:00.030 --> 13:01.510
Arrest this assassin!

13:01.870 --> 13:02.790
Who are you?

13:03.160 --> 13:04.220
What are you doing?

13:04.480 --> 13:06.000
This is the Crown Prince's Mansion.

13:06.000 --> 13:07.580
I am the Crown Prince's person.

13:07.580 --> 13:09.110
The Crown Prince's person?

13:17.960 --> 13:20.840
I often visit the Crown Prince's Mansion.

13:21.200 --> 13:22.910
Why have I never met you?

13:23.790 --> 13:25.320
The Crown Prince went north for a tour.

13:25.320 --> 13:28.030
It is not surprising
that he brought back a woman.

13:28.030 --> 13:29.100
And who are you?

13:29.550 --> 13:31.360
Does the Crown Prince need to report

13:31.360 --> 13:33.360
where he goes and what he does to you?

13:33.360 --> 13:34.360
In that case,

13:35.210 --> 13:36.690
please enter the palace

13:37.670 --> 13:41.270
and explain the whole story
to Her Majesty with the Crown Prince.

13:44.320 --> 13:45.080
Take her!

14:06.470 --> 14:07.730
She is not an assassin.

14:08.750 --> 14:10.000
She is Princess Fu.

14:10.000 --> 14:13.840
Your Highness, didn't you enter
the palace to pay respects to Her Majesty?

14:13.840 --> 14:15.360
Why are you here?

14:15.840 --> 14:17.870
I just returned to Tangjing today.

14:18.150 --> 14:19.750
I suddenly had a stomachache

14:19.910 --> 14:21.790
and feared being disrespectful
to my mother.

14:21.790 --> 14:23.240
So I turned back halfway.

14:24.000 --> 14:25.600
Unexpectedly, I ran into you

14:26.780 --> 14:28.750
having a misunderstanding
with Princess Fu.

14:28.750 --> 14:29.790
Princess Fu?

14:29.790 --> 14:30.550
Lord Zhan,

14:30.960 --> 14:33.360
this woman is not the assassin
you speak of,

14:33.910 --> 14:35.600
but the daughter of the Prince of Pingnan

14:35.600 --> 14:38.030
I found after going through
many hardships,

14:38.030 --> 14:39.120
Princess Fu.

14:40.320 --> 14:41.250
Seven years ago,

14:42.080 --> 14:44.740
the Prince of Pingnan
went to war with his family

14:44.750 --> 14:46.390
and died in battle.

14:47.430 --> 14:49.550
Princess Fu was separated
from them ever since,

14:49.550 --> 14:51.080
and there was no news of her.

14:51.600 --> 14:53.200
My trip to Great Yan this time

14:53.550 --> 14:54.120
was exactly because

14:54.120 --> 14:56.250
I heard of Princess Fu's whereabouts,

14:56.550 --> 14:58.880
and I went specifically to bring her back.

14:59.670 --> 15:00.550
At that time, Lord Zhan, you

15:00.550 --> 15:03.390
hadn't yet entered
the palace to serve Her Majesty,

15:03.390 --> 15:05.600
so you know very little about this matter.

15:05.600 --> 15:06.330
Why don't you

15:07.100 --> 15:09.100
go ask my mother?

15:09.550 --> 15:11.270
She'll naturally

15:12.270 --> 15:13.790
clear your doubts.

15:14.120 --> 15:16.120
Your Highness, given what you said,

15:16.480 --> 15:18.200
I will return to the palace

15:18.870 --> 15:21.150
and ask Her Majesty for clarification.

15:23.960 --> 15:24.720
Excuse me.

15:25.640 --> 15:26.230
Let's go.

15:52.870 --> 15:53.630
How is he?

15:53.920 --> 15:55.350
Wake up, wake up.

15:56.120 --> 15:56.960
He's dying.

16:05.150 --> 16:06.010
General Cheng.

16:07.240 --> 16:08.720
We have lost our way.

16:09.360 --> 16:10.290
If we keep going,

16:11.200 --> 16:12.960
we probably won't be able to hold on,

16:12.960 --> 16:15.020
and none of us will make it back alive.

16:16.150 --> 16:17.750
Are you sure it's just ahead?

16:20.270 --> 16:21.270
It's just ahead.

16:22.480 --> 16:25.480
The Altar of Fire
at the top of Mount Hei is right ahead.

16:25.870 --> 16:28.670
As long as we place
His Majesty on the Altar of Fire,

16:29.140 --> 16:31.870
His Majesty will be protected
by the gods of Great Yan

16:31.870 --> 16:33.870
and will surely come back to life.

16:38.870 --> 16:40.070
Keep moving forward.

16:40.370 --> 16:41.030
Yes.

17:03.360 --> 17:04.440
This is the place.

17:06.359 --> 17:08.440
This is the Altar of Fire.

17:13.000 --> 17:14.640
His Majesty will be saved.

18:33.640 --> 18:35.240
-His Majesty!
-His Majesty!

20:17.030 --> 20:18.680
Who was that eunuch just now?

20:19.160 --> 20:20.070
How dare he be so bossy

20:20.070 --> 20:21.800
in the Crown Prince's Mansion?

20:22.070 --> 20:23.510
Zhan Ziyu is not a eunuch.

20:24.160 --> 20:25.880
He is the Grand Minister of Rites,

20:25.880 --> 20:27.550
a close minister to my mother.

20:28.270 --> 20:29.670
Most of the things he does

20:30.400 --> 20:32.070
are my mother's ideas.

20:34.790 --> 20:35.750
Your mother?

20:38.960 --> 20:39.920
Your Highness.

20:41.070 --> 20:41.930
Your Highness.

20:43.750 --> 20:44.610
Your Highness.

20:44.640 --> 20:45.500
Your Highness.

20:48.400 --> 20:51.030
-Your Highness.
-Your Highness.

20:51.860 --> 20:55.970
-Your Highness.
-Your Highness.

20:56.000 --> 20:56.960
You're all here.

20:56.960 --> 20:58.750
-Your Highness.
-Your Highness.

20:58.750 --> 21:00.750
Why didn't you tell me you were back?

21:00.920 --> 21:01.830
Your Highness,

21:01.920 --> 21:03.590
did you forget about me?

21:03.590 --> 21:04.510
Of course not.

21:04.510 --> 21:05.510
Then look at this.

21:05.790 --> 21:07.110
This is the sachet I made for you

21:07.110 --> 21:08.880
when you were away.

21:08.880 --> 21:09.680
Smell it.

21:11.270 --> 21:12.130
Your Highness.

21:12.400 --> 21:13.310
Your Highness, you must be tired.

21:13.310 --> 21:14.240
Let's go inside and sit down.

21:14.240 --> 21:14.960
-Your Highness.
-Your Highness.

21:14.960 --> 21:15.960
-Your Highness.
-Your Highness.

21:15.960 --> 21:17.590
-Your Highness.
-Your Highness.

21:17.590 --> 21:18.400
-Your Highness.
-Here.

21:18.400 --> 21:20.060
This is the shawl I made for you

21:20.240 --> 21:22.400
when you were away.

21:23.830 --> 21:25.440
I designed it myself.

21:25.680 --> 21:27.080
You can't buy it outside.

21:27.310 --> 21:28.920
I also made one for myself.

21:28.940 --> 21:31.010
We can wear them together later.

21:35.720 --> 21:36.310
Beauty.

21:37.550 --> 21:38.610
Why are you crying?

21:39.000 --> 21:42.160
I saw that your face
was not as rosy as before.

21:42.750 --> 21:46.110
You must have been exhausted in Great Yan.

21:46.400 --> 21:48.460
It broke my heart to see you like this.

21:50.480 --> 21:51.310
Who is she?

21:53.160 --> 21:54.880
-Who is she?
-Who is she?

21:55.640 --> 21:57.500
-Your Highness.
-Your Highness.

21:57.680 --> 21:59.160
She... she...

22:00.160 --> 22:01.200
She is...

22:10.390 --> 22:11.150
Who are you?

22:11.170 --> 22:12.030
Tell us the truth.

22:12.030 --> 22:13.160
She's a vixen.

22:14.440 --> 22:16.270
-Little vixen.
-Little vixen.

22:18.010 --> 22:19.720
-Your Highness.
-Your Highness.

22:19.720 --> 22:21.110
Since you're unfaithful

22:21.110 --> 22:22.440
and have a little vixen,

22:22.830 --> 22:25.110
we will let them be.

22:25.310 --> 22:26.440
If we are here,

22:26.470 --> 22:27.720
the little vixen can't be.

22:27.720 --> 22:29.640
If she is here, we won't be.

22:29.640 --> 22:30.350
Your Highness,

22:30.350 --> 22:32.750
you can go be a couple
with the little vixen!

22:32.830 --> 22:33.640
Sisters,

22:33.960 --> 22:34.490
let's go.

22:44.320 --> 22:47.160
[Minglu,
Chief Maid of the Crown Prince's Mansion]

22:47.590 --> 22:48.270
By the way,

22:48.590 --> 22:49.710
where is Lady Ziming?

22:49.710 --> 22:51.020
Why haven't I seen her since I returned?

22:51.020 --> 22:52.620
-Lady Ziming?
-Lady Ziming?

22:53.310 --> 22:54.240
Your Highness,

22:54.440 --> 22:56.480
she hasn't seen you for days.

22:56.790 --> 22:57.920
She worried too much

22:58.680 --> 23:00.340
and suffered a heart illness.

23:00.720 --> 23:01.650
A heart illness?

23:03.000 --> 23:03.830
I see.

23:04.400 --> 23:05.720
She must be missing me.

23:06.480 --> 23:07.510
Tell your lady

23:07.830 --> 23:09.490
that I will go see her tonight.

23:15.400 --> 23:17.260
This is the room prepared for you.

23:17.310 --> 23:18.680
Before His Highness returned,

23:18.680 --> 23:20.680
he had sent someone to arrange this.

23:21.030 --> 23:22.690
But it was prepared in a hurry.

23:22.790 --> 23:24.650
I will come to tidy it up tomorrow.

23:30.960 --> 23:32.920
Please thank the Crown Prince for me.

23:32.920 --> 23:34.510
I have always preferred things
to be simple.

23:34.510 --> 23:35.370
This is enough.

23:38.110 --> 23:40.830
May I ask how I should address you?

23:41.440 --> 23:43.370
I am the chief maid of this mansion.

23:43.590 --> 23:45.200
If you need anything, Princess,

23:45.200 --> 23:46.330
just tell the maids,

23:46.590 --> 23:47.790
and I will prepare it.

23:48.030 --> 23:48.920
If not,

23:49.440 --> 23:51.570
you won't need to address me normally.

24:07.270 --> 24:08.270
What Princess Fu?

24:09.660 --> 24:11.920
Princess Fu has been dead for a long time.

24:12.160 --> 24:15.160
Seven years ago,
the Prince of Pingnan went against me

24:15.270 --> 24:18.110
and publicly opposed my involvement
in state affairs at court.

24:18.110 --> 24:21.070
So I had His Majesty send him
to fight on the southern border,

24:21.070 --> 24:22.440
and he sacrificed
his life for the country.

24:22.440 --> 24:23.880
Princess Fu
and Princess Consort of Pingnan

24:23.880 --> 24:25.720
also went to the southern border with him.

24:25.720 --> 24:28.120
They have long been dead,
leaving no trace.

24:28.790 --> 24:31.250
Could it be that the woman
is not Princess Fu?

24:31.980 --> 24:33.440
Then why did the Crown Prince...

24:33.440 --> 24:35.000
The Crown Prince is a womanizer.

24:35.000 --> 24:36.350
It's not surprising

24:36.640 --> 24:38.200
that he would just find any woman.

24:38.200 --> 24:40.640
But you said this woman
knows martial arts,

24:41.030 --> 24:43.430
and the Crown Prince
even defied me for her.

24:44.680 --> 24:46.720
That is somewhat unexpected.

24:46.930 --> 24:48.580
Your Majesty, do you mean

24:49.200 --> 24:51.640
that the woman's identity is suspicious?

24:53.160 --> 24:56.310
His Majesty's health
won't last for many more days.

24:56.880 --> 24:58.000
Once he dies,

24:58.880 --> 25:01.880
whether Li Ce remains
the Crown Prince or is deposed

25:02.480 --> 25:04.480
will be entirely up to me.

25:05.400 --> 25:06.400
At this critical juncture,

25:06.400 --> 25:08.110
no matter who this woman is,

25:08.480 --> 25:10.080
she is of utmost importance.

25:10.200 --> 25:12.030
If she is just a romantic affair,

25:12.030 --> 25:13.640
we will report it to the Emperor

25:13.640 --> 25:16.170
and make it known
to the whole imperial court.

25:16.360 --> 25:18.310
If there really is a hidden agenda,

25:18.870 --> 25:20.110
don't blame me

25:22.320 --> 25:24.920
for not showing mercy
to my own flesh and blood.

25:25.720 --> 25:26.590
I understand.

25:27.470 --> 25:30.800
I will keep a close eye on
the Crown Prince's Mansion for you.

26:13.200 --> 26:14.600
It's getting cold again.

26:15.160 --> 26:16.560
You once promised me

26:18.800 --> 26:20.980
that you'd watch the snow
with me every year.

26:20.980 --> 26:23.470
[Spirit Tablet
of the Late Crown Prince Maocheng]

26:21.990 --> 26:23.390
The snow is about to fall,

26:23.810 --> 26:25.330
but you're not by my side.

26:29.110 --> 26:31.640
It is you, the Emperor,
who broke your promise

26:31.830 --> 26:33.760
and killed Crown Prince Maocheng.

26:34.270 --> 26:35.800
Since you are so heartless,

26:36.400 --> 26:38.130
don't blame me for being cruel.

27:17.270 --> 27:18.110
Princess Fu.

27:20.510 --> 27:21.440
It's so late.

27:22.110 --> 27:23.000
Crown Prince, shouldn't you be going

27:23.000 --> 27:24.460
to that sick lady's place?

27:26.470 --> 27:28.350
What are you talking about, Princess Fu?

27:28.350 --> 27:30.400
I have always loved you the most.

27:30.840 --> 27:34.120
I will stay in your room tonight.

27:35.240 --> 27:35.570
Ouch!

27:35.640 --> 27:36.240
Princess,

27:36.440 --> 27:37.400
what are you doing?

27:37.400 --> 27:38.200
Let me ask you,

27:38.880 --> 27:40.000
who is Princess Fu?

27:40.400 --> 27:41.680
Why did you say I am her?

27:43.960 --> 27:44.490
Careful.

27:44.960 --> 27:45.890
Walls have ears.

27:46.920 --> 27:48.380
Stop being so mysterious.

27:58.070 --> 27:58.840
Fu,

27:58.960 --> 28:00.200
don't be angry.

28:00.480 --> 28:00.940
They...

28:01.200 --> 28:02.640
They were all rewarded by my mother

28:02.640 --> 28:03.790
while you were away.

28:04.590 --> 28:06.240
Aren't you back now?

28:06.330 --> 28:07.260
What's going on?

28:08.160 --> 28:09.760
I'll make a long story short.

28:10.110 --> 28:10.880
I am

28:11.400 --> 28:13.880
a useless Crown Prince with no power.

28:14.190 --> 28:16.160
Although there are many beauties
in this mansion,

28:16.160 --> 28:18.220
they were all given to me by my mother.

28:18.270 --> 28:19.070
Normally,

28:19.790 --> 28:20.810
their duty

28:20.830 --> 28:22.290
is not only to entertain me

28:22.590 --> 28:24.790
and make me indulge in luxury

28:25.200 --> 28:26.590
and sensual pleasures

28:27.720 --> 28:29.790
but also to report my every word and deed

28:29.790 --> 28:31.240
to my mother.

28:31.960 --> 28:33.000
As for Fu,

28:34.030 --> 28:36.240
she was the princess
of the Prince of Pingnan

28:36.240 --> 28:37.700
and someone I used to like.

28:38.440 --> 28:39.110
Now,

28:40.960 --> 28:42.240
she is no longer alive.

28:43.350 --> 28:45.110
You do look a bit like her.

28:45.350 --> 28:47.080
I borrowed her identity for you

28:47.640 --> 28:50.160
to protect you as much as possible.

28:50.830 --> 28:51.790
In that case,

28:52.510 --> 28:53.720
I misunderstood you.

28:54.640 --> 28:56.830
Since you are pretending
to be Princess Fu,

28:56.830 --> 28:57.590
from now on,

28:58.920 --> 29:00.980
I will have to stay here for the night.

29:03.880 --> 29:04.920
You have no idea.

29:05.310 --> 29:06.440
What I fear the most

29:06.440 --> 29:07.970
is being with them at night.

29:08.200 --> 29:08.720
But

29:09.350 --> 29:10.310
you're here now.

29:11.790 --> 29:12.720
What do you mean?

29:14.070 --> 29:15.270
Being with you—

29:18.000 --> 29:19.110
Princess, Princess!

29:19.110 --> 29:19.710
Be gentle!

29:19.880 --> 29:20.880
Princess, it hurts!

29:20.880 --> 29:21.410
It hurts!

29:45.350 --> 29:46.030
Let me do it.

30:06.790 --> 30:07.750
It's getting late.

30:07.750 --> 30:08.960
Are we still hitting the road?

30:08.960 --> 30:10.920
Lord Zhao finally found Chu Qiao.

30:10.940 --> 30:12.280
We must travel overnight

30:12.280 --> 30:14.130
to pass this news to Lord Muhe.

30:14.480 --> 30:15.340
We can't delay.

30:15.550 --> 30:16.310
Sir,

30:16.720 --> 30:17.400
the bill.

30:48.510 --> 30:49.310
Who are you?

30:49.830 --> 30:50.760
What do you want?

30:52.680 --> 30:54.000
If you dare tell what you know

30:54.000 --> 30:55.070
to the Muhe family,

30:56.030 --> 30:58.160
I'll make sure you never speak again.

31:01.680 --> 31:04.160
Zhuge Yue. Zhuge Yue.

31:04.880 --> 31:05.720
Zhuge Yue.

31:08.150 --> 31:10.260
Zhuge Yue. Zhuge Yue.

31:13.200 --> 31:13.920
Zhuge Yue.

31:15.070 --> 31:16.830
Zhuge Yue, where are you going?

31:17.640 --> 31:18.270
Don't go.

31:18.470 --> 31:20.030
Zhuge Yue, don't go.

31:20.750 --> 31:22.400
Zhuge Yue. Zhuge Yue.

31:22.920 --> 31:24.050
Where have you gone?

31:24.240 --> 31:24.840
Come back.

31:24.960 --> 31:25.720
Zhuge Yue.

31:26.310 --> 31:27.110
Zhuge Yue!

31:30.110 --> 31:30.680
Fu.

31:31.520 --> 31:32.170
Fu.

31:33.110 --> 31:33.910
What's wrong?

31:37.920 --> 31:38.640
Was I just

31:39.270 --> 31:40.750
talking in my sleep?

31:42.480 --> 31:43.200
Just now,

31:43.640 --> 31:45.570
you kept calling Zhuge Yue's name.

31:46.000 --> 31:47.400
I was afraid someone would hear,

31:47.400 --> 31:48.270
so I woke you up.

31:48.960 --> 31:50.360
What did you dream about?

31:50.750 --> 31:51.550
Nothing.

31:53.000 --> 31:55.130
Ever since I woke up at the frozen lake,

31:55.430 --> 31:57.430
my dreams have been mostly the same.

31:58.110 --> 31:58.720
Who is it?

32:13.000 --> 32:13.790
Qiao.

32:15.270 --> 32:17.250
You are indeed unmatched in martial arts

32:17.250 --> 32:18.380
and dashingly cool.

32:18.470 --> 32:19.230
Shut up.

32:34.160 --> 32:36.020
This hidden weapon is poisonous.

32:41.270 --> 32:42.130
What happened?

32:42.750 --> 32:43.680
In this mansion,

32:44.200 --> 32:45.510
someone wants my life.

32:45.620 --> 32:46.940
Hansha Darts...

32:48.160 --> 32:50.720
They're the hidden weapon
of the Muhe family of Great Yong.

32:50.720 --> 32:51.590
I'm afraid

32:52.200 --> 32:53.640
they didn't come for you.

32:53.800 --> 32:55.610
[Zuiyue Restaurant]

32:56.200 --> 32:57.200
Guests.

32:59.920 --> 33:00.550
Remember,

33:00.960 --> 33:03.420
sometimes
hearing is more real than seeing.

33:03.590 --> 33:04.650
When you can't see,

33:04.870 --> 33:06.870
you can actually find what you want.

33:26.960 --> 33:27.880
Great,

33:27.290 --> 33:30.190
[Zhao Kuo, Envoy of Great Yong]

33:28.640 --> 33:30.350
you delivered yourself to me.

34:03.680 --> 34:04.350
Chu Qiao,

34:04.960 --> 34:07.640
I knew you were still alive.

34:08.670 --> 34:09.920
I just didn't expect

34:10.110 --> 34:12.190
that after hiding
in the Crown Prince's Mansion,

34:12.190 --> 34:14.190
you would dare to come meet me alone.

34:14.760 --> 34:15.889
If I hadn't shown up,

34:16.350 --> 34:18.179
would you really have spared me?

34:18.840 --> 34:20.030
You are right.

34:20.840 --> 34:22.440
Back then, you and Yan Xun joined forces

34:22.440 --> 34:24.239
to kill Young Master Muhe Xifeng

34:24.670 --> 34:27.110
and took the opportunity
to bring down the Wei family.

34:27.110 --> 34:28.760
Guess who in Great Yong

34:29.360 --> 34:31.670
wants you dead more, the Muhe family

34:32.190 --> 34:35.000
or the Wei family?

34:35.590 --> 34:38.670
It's a pity that your worthless life

34:39.400 --> 34:41.659
isn't enough to repay Young Master Muhe.

34:42.550 --> 34:44.000
I will kill you first

34:44.000 --> 34:46.060
and then kill that scoundrel Yan Xun!

35:07.110 --> 35:09.840
Aren't you the most capable general
in Great Yan?

35:10.710 --> 35:11.800
Aren't you the invincible leader

35:11.800 --> 35:13.710
of the Xiuli Army?

35:17.570 --> 35:19.610
I will send you to hell right now!

35:36.550 --> 35:37.150
Xing.

35:37.960 --> 35:39.000
Xing, wake up.

36:05.700 --> 36:07.610
♪ On the water ♪

36:07.640 --> 36:09.350
♪ Countless ♪

36:09.370 --> 36:11.060
♪ Ripples rise ♪

36:13.350 --> 36:15.410
♪ Through the mortal world ♪

36:14.810 --> 36:15.560
Zhuge Yue.

36:15.440 --> 36:18.860
♪ With meetings and goodbyes ♪

36:20.770 --> 36:23.110
♪ How unfair fate is ♪

36:22.920 --> 36:24.070
I've seen you.

36:23.140 --> 36:28.130
♪ It gave all the memories back to you ♪

36:25.840 --> 36:26.760
Zhuge Yue,

36:28.450 --> 36:30.290
♪ Yet left me ♪

36:28.600 --> 36:29.690
I've seen you.

36:30.700 --> 36:34.280
♪ Stuck right here ♪

36:36.210 --> 36:37.420
♪ Rain falls down ♪

36:38.000 --> 36:39.390
♪ Lingering thoughts ♪

36:39.940 --> 36:42.180
♪ Awake once more ♪

36:43.870 --> 36:46.040
♪ Let the wind shape ♪

36:46.080 --> 36:49.740
♪ Another me ♪

36:51.670 --> 36:53.670
♪ How can I escape ♪

36:53.690 --> 36:58.460
♪ All the reflections that hold you? ♪

36:59.080 --> 37:02.050
♪ Behind the illusions
of the moon in water ♪

36:59.400 --> 37:00.230
Zhuge Yue.

37:02.630 --> 37:04.150
I've finally seen you.

37:02.970 --> 37:05.680
♪ I wait to sink deep ♪

37:05.590 --> 37:07.510
Today is exactly the 14th day.

37:05.700 --> 37:10.120
♪ May fortune smile on all below ♪

37:08.470 --> 37:10.400
The Huotu water you gave me worked.

37:10.320 --> 37:13.910
♪ Just to hear when you'll come home ♪

37:13.070 --> 37:14.480
I know you are still alive,

37:14.360 --> 37:16.360
♪ Braving schemes alone ♪

37:15.060 --> 37:17.310
and I also know you sent the Huotu water.

37:16.380 --> 37:18.100
♪ Treading through thorns ♪

37:17.810 --> 37:18.640
Zhuge Yue,

37:18.120 --> 37:20.720
♪ Searching for your name ♪

37:19.200 --> 37:20.800
you've been alive all along.

37:20.800 --> 37:25.530
♪ Till storms rise again ♪

37:21.630 --> 37:23.630
But why have you been hiding from me?

37:25.550 --> 37:29.440
♪ Not a single regret remains ♪

37:28.710 --> 37:31.230
You risked getting hurt to kill Zhao Kuo

37:29.460 --> 37:31.460
♪ Melt the ice ♪

37:31.480 --> 37:33.480
♪ That fate has wrought ♪

37:31.760 --> 37:33.400
and used your internal energy
to hold your breath,

37:33.400 --> 37:35.880
making me think you were dying.

37:33.510 --> 37:38.720
♪ Let the night ♪

37:37.750 --> 37:39.460
Was it just to draw me out?

37:39.670 --> 37:40.280
Yes.

37:40.060 --> 37:45.380
♪ Forever glow ♪

37:40.550 --> 37:42.150
Everyone said you were dead,

37:43.070 --> 37:44.470
but I knew you were alive.

37:46.480 --> 37:48.550
I could feel you by my side.

37:49.360 --> 37:51.360
If it weren't for you protecting me,

37:51.550 --> 37:52.510
Li Ce and I

37:53.150 --> 37:55.750
wouldn't have made it
to Biantang so smoothly.

37:56.760 --> 37:57.550
Xing.

37:58.540 --> 37:59.460
Do you know

38:02.360 --> 38:04.020
the Xiuli Army died in battle,

38:05.590 --> 38:08.050
and Miss Zhong was also
killed by Cheng Yuan?

38:10.440 --> 38:11.190
I know.

38:12.480 --> 38:13.480
Do you know

38:14.960 --> 38:16.070
I almost thought

38:17.290 --> 38:18.930
that I got Zhong Yu,

38:19.590 --> 38:20.840
the Xiuli Army,

38:22.170 --> 38:24.370
and the person I care about most killed?

38:30.630 --> 38:33.360
Do you still remember
the day I left for Great Yan?

38:34.230 --> 38:35.230
You told me

38:36.500 --> 38:37.670
you needed me.

38:40.280 --> 38:41.320
Now,

38:41.880 --> 38:42.760
Zhuge Yue,

38:45.680 --> 38:47.240
can you stay for me?

39:14.920 --> 39:16.480
General Huan, you're tired
from putting down the rebellion.

39:16.480 --> 39:17.900
Go back and rest.

39:19.440 --> 39:21.320
Are you sure it was a woman
who entered your room?

39:21.320 --> 39:22.630
-As the King commands!
-As the King commands!

39:22.630 --> 39:25.360
I am already living like a ghost.

39:25.360 --> 39:27.150
What does it matter if I die?

39:27.320 --> 39:28.760
She looks a bit like...

39:28.960 --> 39:32.190
the escaped slave
Great Yan and Great Yong are hunting down,

39:32.190 --> 39:33.070
Chu Qiao.
